0 * * * * python /home/pi/camera.py

camera.py koodi on:
from picamera import PiCamera 
from time import sleep

camera = PiCamera()
tiedosto = 'valvonta.jpg'

camera.start_preview()
sleep(1)
camera.capture(tiedosto)
camera.stop_preview()
